<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Termux Reconnector Admin</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0f172a;
            color: #f8fafc;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #38bdf8, #818cf8);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: #1e293b;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .card h3 {
            margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        .card .value {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #f8fafc;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .status-dot {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }

        .online {
            background-color: #22c55e;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px #22c55e;
        }

        .offline {
            background-color: #ef4444;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px #ef4444;
        }

        .btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #3b82f6);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 8px -1px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.6);
        }

        .btn.stop {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #b91c1c);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
        }

        .btn.stop:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 6px 8px -1px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.6);
        }

        .logs {
            background-color: #1e293b;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .logs h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #38bdf8;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #334155;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            text-align: left;
        }

        th,
        td {
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #334155;
        }

        th {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        a.link {
            color: #38bdf8;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a.link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .admin-section {
            background-color: #1e293b;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .admin-section h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #818cf8;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #334155;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .form-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .form-group {
            background: #0f172a;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .form-group h4 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #f8fafc;
        }

        .form-group p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        .form-group input {
            padding: 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
            background: #1e293b;
            color: white;
            outline: none;
        }

        .form-group input:focus {
            border-color: #38bdf8;
        }

        .btn-small {
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .notification {
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .notify-success {
            background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid #22c55e;
            color: #4ade80;
        }

        .notify-error {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid #ef4444;
            color: #f87171;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Termux Admin Panel</h1>
            <p>Discord Bot & HWID Session Manager</p>
        </div>

        <% if (typeof alert !=='undefined' && alert) { %>
            <div class="notification <%= alert.type === 'success' ? 'notify-success' : 'notify-error' %>">
                <%= alert.message %>
            </div>
            <% } %>

                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Bot Status</h3>
                        <p class="value">
                            <span class="status-dot <%= state.botOnline ? 'online' : 'offline' %>"></span>
                            <%= state.botOnline ? 'Online' : 'Offline' %>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Active Keys Generated</h3>
                        <p class="value">
                            <%= state.totalKeysGenerated %>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Discord Connected</h3>
                        <p class="value">
                            <%= userTag %>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="controls">
                    <form action="/api/bot/toggle" method="POST">
                        <% if (state.botOnline) { %>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn stop">Shut Down Bot</button>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <button type="submit" class="btn">Start Discord Bot</button>
                                <% } %>
                    </form>
                    <button class="btn" onclick="location.reload()">Refresh Data</button>
                </div>

                <div class="logs">
                    <h2>Recent Hardware Key Generations</h2>
                    <% if (state.recentKeys.length===0) { %>
                        <p style="text-align:center; color:#94a3b8;">No keys generated yet.</p>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <table>
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Time</th>
                                        <th>Discord Account</th>
                                        <th>Platorelay Secure Link</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <% state.recentKeys.forEach(function(log) { %>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>
                                                <%= log.time %>
                                            </td>
                                            <td><strong>
                                                    <%= log.discordId %>
                                                </strong></td>
                                            <td><a href="<%= log.link %>" target="_blank" class="link">View Generation
                                                    Link</a></td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <% }); %>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                            <% } %>
                </div>

                <div class="admin-section">
                    <h2>Advanced Key Management</h2>
                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <h4>Generate Instant Key</h4>
                            <p>Bypass Discord and get a direct Platorelay link.</p>
                            <form action="/api/admin/create-key" method="POST"
                                style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.5rem; margin-top:0.5rem;">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-small">Generate Link</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group">
                            <h4>Delete / Blacklist Key</h4>
                            <p>Permanently invalidate a specific key.</p>
                            <form action="/api/admin/delete-key" method="POST"
                                style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.5rem; margin-top:0.5rem;">
                                <input type="text" name="key" placeholder="Enter Platoboost Key" required>
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-small stop">Delete Key</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group">
                            <h4>Forcible HWID Reset</h4>
                            <p>Unbind a key from a user's device if they can't use Discord.</p>
                            <form action="/api/admin/reset-hwid" method="POST"
                                style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.5rem; margin-top:0.5rem;">
                                <input type="text" name="key" placeholder="Enter Platoboost Key" required>
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-small">Reset Binding</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>